and because of great servitude: she dwelleth among the heathen, she findeth no rest: all her persecutors overtook her between the straits.","year":-588},{"id":"recHd6CBwVtA30RZs","ref":"Lam.1.4","text":"The ways of Zion do mourn, because none come to the solemn feasts: all her gates are desolate: her priests sigh, her virgins are afflicted, and she is in bitterness.","year":-588},{"id":"recnmOLHWmOW9h5N4","ref":"Lam.1.5","text":"Her adversaries are the chief, her enemies prosper; for the LORD hath afflicted her for the multitude of her transgressions: her children are gone into captivity before the enemy.","year":-588},{"id":"reccIP02L88RMjo4w","ref":"Lam.1.6","text":"And from the daughter of Zion all her beauty is departed: her princes are become like harts that find no pasture, and they are gone without strength before the pursuer.","year":-588}]}
